#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:173
msgid ""
"No JavaScript is involved — all detection and suppression happens server-"
"side in FreeMarker before the HTML reaches the browser."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:175
msgid "Cancel link"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:177
msgid ""
"Both citizen (test/fallback) and caseworker login forms include a \"← Terug "
"naar inlogkeuze\" link below the submit button. It uses `history.go(-2)` to "
"skip over the `/auth` intermediate route:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:179
msgid ""
"<div id=\"kc-cancel-container\">\n"
"    <a id=\"kc-cancel\" href=\"${client.baseUrl!'/'}\"\n"
"       onclick=\"history.go(-2); return false;\" tabindex=\"7\">\n"
"        <!-- left-arrow SVG -->\n"
"        Terug naar inlogkeuze\n"
"    </a>\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:189
msgid ""
"The `href` fallback (`client.baseUrl`) points to the frontend root URL "
"configured in Keycloak Admin → Clients → `ronl-business-api` → Root URL. "
"This is only used if JavaScript is disabled. The `history.go(-2)` skip is "
"necessary because the browser history stack at this point is: `/ → /auth → "
"[Keycloak]`, and `history.back()` would land on `/auth`, which immediately "
"redirects back to Keycloak."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:191
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Container restart required after theme changes\" Keycloak caches "
"theme templates at startup. Any change to `.ftl` or `.css` files requires a "
"container restart to take effect — regardless of whether Keycloak is running "
"in development or production mode. Theme changes do not require an image "
"rebuild."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:196
msgid "Deploying to ACC"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:198
msgid "Step 1 — Prepare theme files"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:200
msgid "On your local machine:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:202
msgid ""
"cd ~/Development/ronl-business-api\n"
"\n"
"# Create theme tarball\n"
"cd deployment/vm/keycloak/themes\n"
"tar -czf ronl-theme.tar.gz ronl/\n"
"\n"
"# Upload to VM\n"
"scp ronl-theme.tar.gz user@your-vm:/tmp/"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:213
msgid "Step 2 — Deploy theme on VM"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:215
msgid "SSH into the VM:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:217
msgid ""
"ssh user@your-vm\n"
"\n"
"# Create themes directory (one-time setup)\n"
"sudo mkdir -p /opt/keycloak/themes\n"
"sudo chown 1000:1000 /opt/keycloak/themes\n"
"sudo chmod 755 /opt/keycloak/themes\n"
"\n"
"# Extract theme\n"
"cd /tmp\n"
"tar -xzf ronl-theme.tar.gz\n"
"\n"
"# Install theme\n"
"sudo rm -rf /opt/keycloak/themes/ronl\n"
"sudo mv ronl /opt/keycloak/themes/\n"
"\n"
"# Set permissions (Keycloak runs as UID 1000)\n"
"sudo chown -R 1000:1000 /opt/keycloak/themes/ronl\n"
"sudo chmod -R 755 /opt/keycloak/themes/ronl\n"
"sudo find /opt/keycloak/themes/ronl -type f -exec chmod 644 {} \\;\n"
"\n"
"# Verify\n"
"ls -la /opt/keycloak/themes/ronl/login/\n"
"\n"
"# Cleanup\n"
"rm /tmp/ronl-theme.tar.gz"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:245
msgid "Step 3 — Update docker-compose.yml"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:247
msgid "The docker-compose.yml must mount the themes directory:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:249
msgid ""
"services:\n"
"  keycloak-acc:\n"
"    image: quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:23.0\n"
"    container_name: keycloak-acc\n"
"    volumes:\n"
"      - ./ronl-realm.json:/opt/keycloak/data/import/ronl-realm.json:ro\n"
"      - keycloak-acc-data:/opt/keycloak/data\n"
"      - /opt/keycloak/themes:/opt/keycloak/themes:ro  # Theme volume mount"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:260
msgid "**Update on VM:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:262
msgid ""
"cd /home/steven/keycloak/acc\n"
"\n"
"# Backup current config\n"
"cp docker-compose.yml docker-compose.yml.backup\n"
"\n"
"# Edit to add theme volume\n"
"nano docker-compose.yml\n"
"# Add: - /opt/keycloak/themes:/opt/keycloak/themes:ro\n"
"\n"
"# Recreate container to apply volume mount\n"
"docker compose down\n"
"docker compose up -d\n"
"\n"
"# Wait for startup\n"
"sleep 30\n"
"\n"
"# Check logs\n"
"docker compose logs keycloak-acc --tail 50"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:283
msgid "Step 4 — Copy configuration files to VM"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:285
msgid ""
"# On local machine\n"
"cd ~/Development/ronl-business-api\n"
"\n"
"# Copy docker-compose.yml\n"
"scp deployment/vm/keycloak/acc/docker-compose.yml user@your-vm:~/keycloak/"
"acc/\n"
"\n"
"# Copy realm file\n"
"scp config/keycloak/ronl-realm.json user@your-vm:~/keycloak/acc/"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:296
msgid "Step 5 — Create environment file"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:298
msgid ""
"# On VM\n"
"cd ~/keycloak/acc\n"
"\n"
"# Generate secure password\n"
"ADMIN_PW=$(openssl rand -base64 32)\n"
"\n"
"# Create .env file\n"
"cat > .env << EOF\n"
"KEYCLOAK_ADMIN_PASSWORD=$ADMIN_PW\n"
"EOF\n"
"\n"
"chmod 600 .env\n"
"\n"
"# Save password securely\n"
"echo \"ACC Admin: $ADMIN_PW\" >> ~/keycloak-passwords-acc.txt\n"
"chmod 600 ~/keycloak-passwords-acc.txt"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:317
msgid "Step 6 — Start Keycloak"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:319
msgid ""
"cd ~/keycloak/acc\n"
"\n"
"# Start services\n"
"docker compose up -d\n"
"\n"
"# Watch logs\n"
"docker compose logs -f keycloak-acc\n"
"\n"
"# Wait for: \"Keycloak started\" and \"Realm 'ronl' imported\""
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:331
msgid "Step 7 — Configure theme in Admin Console"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:333
msgid "**Open Admin Console:** https://acc.keycloak.open-regels.nl/admin"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:334
msgid "**Login** with admin credentials (from `~/keycloak-passwords-acc.txt`)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Ckeycloak.md:335
msgid "**Select realm:** Switch to `ronl` realm (top-left dropdown)"
msgstr ""

